column2: SELECT   sph.plate, sph.mjd, sph.fiberID, s.z,  ge.bptclass, ge.lgm_tot_p5#,   ge.sfr_tot_p5#, ge.specsfr_tot_p5#,  sph.fiberMag_u, sph.fiberMag_g,  sph.fiberMag_i, sph.fiberMag_z,  sph.petroMag_g, sph.petroMag_r,  sph.petroMag_i, sph.modelMag_g,   sph.modelMag_r, sph.modelMag_i FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN galSpecIndx AS gi ON s.specObjID = gi.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra AS ge ON s.specObjID = ge.specObjID  JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sph ON s.specObjID = sph.specObjID  JOIN galSpecLine AS gl ON s.specObjID = gl.specObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.survey = &&&  AND  s.class = &&&  AND  s.snMedian_r > #  AND  s.zWARNING = #
